00:23:58,240 --> 00:24:04,980
 He does not, in anything that is so far from ironic,

546
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:07,100
 tell John what John wants to hear.

547
00:24:07,100 --> 00:24:11,500
 He has the power to change John's circumstance,

548
00:24:11,500 --> 00:24:13,120
 but he chooses not to.

