00:24:17,780 --> 00:24:23,020
 but he knows what John needs.

551
00:24:23,020 --> 00:24:26,980
 He knows that the best way to deal with disappointment

552
00:24:26,980 --> 00:24:29,100
 isn't by changing your circumstances

553
00:24:29,100 --> 00:24:30,940
 to accommodate your faith in God.

554
00:24:30,940 --> 00:24:34,200
 The best way to deal with disappointment

555
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:38,020
 is to grow your faith to deal with any and every circumstance

556
00:24:38,020 --> 00:24:40,580
 that would test you from your God.

557
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:42,940
 He won't give you what you want.

558
00:24:42,940 --> 00:24:44,740
 He will give you what you need.

559
00:24:44,740 --> 00:24:49,460
 And the beauty of it is, it always leads you nearer to him.

560
00:24:49,460 --> 00:24:53,620
 He wants to keep you close by, near to himself,

561
00:24:53,620 --> 00:24:57,460
 not dependent or satisfied or contented

562
00:24:57,460 --> 00:24:59,280
 by anything else in this world.

563
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:02,760
 No, he wants you to cling to him,

564
00:25:02,760 --> 00:25:04,220
 not circumstantial comfort.

