00:27:07,620 --> 00:27:12,620
 Jesus is not in the slightest disappointed with John,

612
00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:15,780
 which should be wildly encouraging to us

613
00:27:15,780 --> 00:27:18,340
 because we may grow disappointed in God from time to time,

